room_title: Escape room "Escape The Zombie" by Crack the Code in Flint
review: First escape room experience. They did an excellent job at putting the room together. Clues were offered as needed.

room_title: Escape room "Escape The Zombie" by Crack the Code in Flint
review: So much fun. The zombie was excellent. It was the greatest.

room_title: Escape room "Escape The Zombie" by Crack the Code in Flint
review: Was a lot of fun. The zombie made it even better! Owner is very nice and friendly.

room_title: Escape room "Escape The Zombie" by Crack the Code in Flint
review: Literally the best escape I've been to so far! The live actor made for such an exciting game! I am looking forward to the next room they open!

room_title: Escape room "Escape The Zombie" by Crack the Code in Flint
review: Our group of 4 escaped with a few minutes remaining (definitely needed the hints) and we had a great time. Lots of challenging puzzles and the zombie was a great addition!
